Balsa E-Mail Client 0.4.8

Copyright (C) 1997-1998 Jay Painter and Stuart Parmenter
See 'COPYING' for licence information.


Please make sure you have the following things:

Glib       >= 1.1.7
GTK        >= 1.1.7
Imlib      >= 1.8.1
gnome-libs >= 0.99

If you do not have these, please check http://www.balsa.net/download.html for
links to these packages.

Build Instructions:

  * To compile:
    # ./configure
    # make

  * To install:
    # make install
